import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; import {Link, useNavigate} from "react-router-dom" function Recipes() { const [recipes, setRecipes] = useState(); const [isModalOpen, setIsModalOpen] = useState(false); let auth = localStorage.getItem("user"); let user = JSON.parse(auth); const navigate = useNavigate(); const openModal = () => { setIsModalOpen(true); }; const closeModal = () => { setIsModalOpen(false); }; useEffect(() => { getRecipes(); }, []); const getRecipes = async () => { let response = await axios.get('http://localhost:5000/recipe/getAllRecipes'); setRecipes(response.data); }; const handleClick = (recipeId)=>{ if(user.premium){ navigate(`/recipe?id=${recipeId}`) } else{ openModal(); } } return (

{recipe.prep_time}

))}
